OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FA river "full of sewage", that is the
OL,8,Fgrim reality along the River Kenfig in
OL,9,FPyle, where wastewater has been
OL,10,Fcaptured continually pumping out of an
OL,11,Foverflow outlet.
OL,13,FThe founder of a nature charity has
OL,14,Fcalled it the "single worst pollution
OL,15,Fincident" he has ever witnessed in the
OL,16,Farea, with reports indicating the
OL,17,Fwaste is heading directly toward Sker
OL,18,FBeach in Porthcawl.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FAlun Phillips, founder of A Peace for
OL,8,FNature, told ITV News that the scale
OL,9,Fof the incident is "atrocious." "What
OL,10,Fis going down this river should not be
OL,11,Fgoing down this river at all," he said.
OL,13,F"The smell is absolutely disgusting,
OL,14,Fit just smells like raw sewage,
OL,15,Fessentially human poo, heading
OL,16,Fstraight downstream.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"As far as we know, it's heading
OL,8,Fstraight down to the beach at Sker and
OL,9,Fcoming right onto the shingle. This is
OL,10,Fnot good, and the fact that it's
OL,11,Fhappening during bathing season makes
OL,12,Fit significantly worse."
OL,14,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water has confirmed
OL,15,Fthe main system in the local area has
OL,16,F"deteriorated" and they currently
OL,17,Fworking on a #13 million project to
OL,18,Freplace 4.5km of sewer main.
OL,26,@vD@Bs{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FIn an update to the local community
OL,8,Fthey conceded that despite "best
OL,9,Fefforts" they have not been able to
OL,10,Ffully prevent discharges.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,13,FWater said: "We are currently working
OL,14,Fon a #13m project to replace 4.5km of
OL,15,Fsewer main in the Kenfig and Port
OL,16,FTalbot area to protect the local
OL,17,Fenvironment following the escalated
OL,18,Fdeterioration of the current main.
OL,26,@tD@Us{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"In the meantime, we have installed a
OL,8,Ffull wastewater treatment process at
OL,9,FMarlas Sewage Pumping Station, marking
OL,10,Fa significant improvement on previous
OL,11,Farrangements of using tankers to
OL,12,Fremove waste. We are continuing to
OL,13,Fclosely monitor performance and are
OL,14,Fassessing the impact of the new
OL,15,Ftreatment process on a daily basis.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"In parallel to this we are laying
OL,8,Fadditional sections of overland
OL,9,Ftemporary pipe. Given the route goes
OL,10,Fthrough land owned by multiple
OL,11,Flandowners and some of it is
OL,12,Fdesignated as sensitive, this is
OL,13,Ftaking some time. We anticipate it
OL,14,Fwill take around two months to
OL,15,Fcomplete.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"We understand this may cause concern;
OL,8,Fwe apologise for the impact the work
OL,9,Fis having on the local area and would
OL,10,Flike to thank our customers for
OL,11,Fbearing with us while we complete this
OL,12,Fessential work."
OL,14,FMembers of the local community have
OL,15,Fcaptured the devastating impact of the
OL,16,Fpollution on local wildlife, sharing
OL,17,Fphotographs of dead fish on the
OL,18,Friverbank.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FGareth Maund, who has lived in the
OL,8,Farea since childhood, said he has been
OL,9,F"picking up dead fish right the way
OL,10,Falong the river."
OL,12,F"There is very, very little life left
OL,13,Fin the riverbed," he said. "We are
OL,14,Fvery angry that Welsh Water, a
OL,15,Fnational company, is doing this to our
OL,16,Fenvironment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"As a young boy, I played in this
OL,8,Friver," he continued. "I've fished,
OL,9,Fwe've swum in the river, we looked for
OL,10,Fbirds' eggs and nests, it has all
OL,11,Fdisappeared. They have killed the
OL,12,Friver; it's absolutely disgusting."
OL,14,FWhat does the data say?
OL,16,FIn 2025 there were 11 serious
OL,17,Fincidents of pollution reported by
OL,18,FWelsh Water. These are cases which
OL,19,Fhave serious environmental impacts.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FThis is an 83% increase from 2024 when
OL,8,Fthere were six serious incidents of
OL,9,Fpollution. This significant increase
OL,10,Fis largely down to the one site near
OL,11,FPort Talbot. A burst pipe has been
OL,12,Freleasing sewage into the Kenfig
OL,13,FNature Reserve which is a Site of
OL,14,FSpecial Scientific Interest.
OL,16,FIn 2025, there was over a thousand
OL,17,Fhours where spills occurred at the
OL,18,FMarlas pump station, which is next to
OL,19,Fthe Kenfig Nature Reserve.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779109902
OL,3,CRiver 'full of sewage' as works
OL,4,Ccarried out replace deteriorated pipe
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FThis is the worst year on record for
OL,8,Fserious incidents of pollution in
OL,9,FWelsh Waters history. The company has
OL,10,Fachieved a red status for the amount
OL,11,Fof serious pollution incidents which
OL,12,Fhave occurred, with only five other
OL,13,Fwater companies in England and Wales
OL,14,Fbeing in the worst category.
OL,16,FWelsh Water was also the worst water
OL,17,Fcompany in England and Wales for self
OL,18,Freporting pollution incidents.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
